select qydj.entcat as "entcat", (case when qydj.datestr = to_char(sysdate-1, 'yyyy-MM-dd') then 'babefore' when qydj.datestr = to_char(sysdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') then 'banow' else '' end) as "datetype", sum(qydj.sl) as "sl" from (select (case when t.entcat='6' then 'nz' else 'qy' end) as entcat, to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') as datestr, count(1) sl from qydj_jbxx_zs t where (to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') = to_char(sysdate - 1, 'yyyy-MM-dd') or to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') = to_char(sysdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd')) and t.entstatus = '2' group by t.entcat, to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') union all select 'gt' as entcat, to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') as datestr, count(1) sl from gtdj_jbxx_zs t where (to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') = to_char(sysdate - 1, 'yyyy-MM-dd') or to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') = to_char(sysdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd')) and t.status = '2' group by to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd')) qydj group by qydj.entcat,qydj.datestr

select (case when t.entcat='6' then 'nz' else 'qy' end) as entcat, count(1) sl from qydj_jbxx_zs t where exists (select 1 from qydj_bgsx_ls qybg where to_char(qybg.altdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') = to_char(sysdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') and t.pripid = qybg.pripid) group by (case when t.entcat='6' then 'nz' else 'qy' end) union all select 'gt' as entcat, count(1) sl from gtdj_jbxx_zs t where exists (select 1 from gtdj_bgsx_ls gtbg where to_char(gtbg.altdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') = to_char(sysdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') and t.pripid = gtbg.pripid)

select (case when t.entcat='6' then 'nz' else 'qy' end) as entcat, count(1) sl from qydj_jbxx_zs t where exists (select 1 from qydj_bgsx_ls qybg where to_char(qybg.altdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') = to_char(sysdate-1, 'yyyy-MM-dd') and t.pripid = qybg.pripid) group by (case when t.entcat='6' then 'nz' else 'qy' end) union all select 'gt' as entcat, count(1) sl from gtdj_jbxx_zs t where exists (select 1 from gtdj_bgsx_ls gtbg where to_char(gtbg.altdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') = to_char(sysdate-1, 'yyyy-MM-dd') and t.pripid = gtbg.pripid)

select qydj.entcat as "entcat", (case when qydj.datestr = to_char(sysdate-1, 'yyyy-MM-dd') then 'zxbefore' when qydj.datestr = to_char(sysdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') then 'zxnow' else '' end) as "datetype", sum(qydj.sl) as "sl" from (select (case when t.entcat='6' then 'nz' else 'qy' end) as entcat, to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') as datestr, count(1) sl from qydj_jbxx_zs t where (to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') = to_char(sysdate - 1, 'yyyy-MM-dd') or to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') = to_char(sysdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd')) and t.entstatus = '3' group by t.entcat, to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') union all select 'gt' as entcat, to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') as datestr, count(1) sl from gtdj_jbxx_zs t where (to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') = to_char(sysdate - 1, 'yyyy-MM-dd') or to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd') = to_char(sysdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd')) and t.status = '3' group by to_char(t.apprdate, 'yyyy-MM-dd')) qydj group by qydj.entcat,qydj.datestr
